      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-mmr-alf-mag       =    "6749050       "
                     go to scn-rec-mmr-600.
           if        rf-mmr-alf-mag (01:03)
                                          not  = "725"
                     go to scn-rec-mmr-200.
       scn-rec-mmr-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Composizione e srittura [kk0]                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Area chiave                             *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
