           move      rf-mmr-tip-mag       to   kk0-tip-mag-2          .
           move      rf-mmr-num-mag       to   kk0-num-mag-2          .
           move      rf-mmr-dat-reg       to   kk0-dat-reg-2          .
           move      rf-mmr-num-prt       to   kk0-num-prt-2          .
           move      rf-mmr-num-prg       to   kk0-num-prg-2          .
