           move      rf-mmr-dat-reg       to   kk0-dat-reg            .
           move      rf-mmr-num-prt       to   kk0-num-prt            .
           move      rf-mmr-num-prg       to   kk0-num-prg            .
           move      rf-mmr-num-mag       to   kk0-num-mag            .
