           add       ww-mms-prg-sca (06)  to   rf-mms-prg-sca (06)    .
      *
           add       ww-mms-prg-car (07)  to   rf-mms-prg-car (07)    .
           add       ww-mms-prg-sca (07)  to   rf-mms-prg-sca (07)    .
      *
           add       ww-mms-prg-car (08)  to   rf-mms-prg-car (08)    .
           add       ww-mms-prg-sca (08)  to   rf-mms-prg-sca (08)    .
      *
           add       ww-mms-prg-car (09)  to   rf-mms-prg-car (09)    .
           add       ww-mms-prg-sca (09)  to   rf-mms-prg-sca (09)    .
      *
           add       ww-mms-prg-car (10)  to   rf-mms-prg-car (10)    .
           add       ww-mms-prg-sca (10)  to   rf-mms-prg-sca (10)    .
      *
           add       ww-mms-prg-car (11)  to   rf-mms-prg-car (11)    .
           add       ww-mms-prg-sca (11)  to   rf-mms-prg-sca (11)    .
      *
           add       ww-mms-prg-car (12)  to   rf-mms-prg-car (12)    .
           add       ww-mms-prg-sca (12)  to   rf-mms-prg-sca (12)    .
      *
           add       ww-mms-dip-ife       to   rf-mms-dip-ife         .
